This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it discusses the use of neuromorphic circuits and synapses in bio-inspired architectures. It may also belong to cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) as it discusses the use of memristive technologies. Additionally, it may belong to cs.EM (Electromagnetics) as it discusses the use of electronic neurons. It may also belong to cs.RO (Robotics) as it discusses the interlinking of biological and artificial neurons. Finally, it may belong to cs.CC (Computational Complexity) as it discusses the computation and memory storage capabilities of synapses.
